The paper deals with image classification using neural networks and distributional semantics, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). It also involves handling small amounts of data and high-dimensional data, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the use of multimodal semantics suggests a connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
